Dialogue: 10,0:00:02.40,0:00:07.01,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Touko. I saw the same thing you did that day.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:09.60,0:00:11.40,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,"The same thing"?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:11.72,0:00:13.51,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,You. Who are you to Touko?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:13.51,0:00:14.53,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:15.27,0:00:17.41,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Did you come here to see her?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:17.41,0:00:18.07,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:18.56,0:00:19.68,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,That all?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:20.29,0:00:21.91,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,How did you know to find her here?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:22.43,0:00:24.48,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,This is where you guys hang out, isn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:24.48,0:00:26.04,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:26.64,0:00:30.10,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting for you at the Kirinkan \NObservation Platform tomorrow at eleven.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:31.12,0:00:31.92,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:31.92,0:00:33.28,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Comment: 10,0:00:34.43,0:02:04.39,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,OP
Dialogue: 10,0:02:06.56,0:02:08.51,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Listen. You don't have\Nto go if you don't want to.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:08.51,0:02:10.62,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Who put {\i1}you{\i0} in charge?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:10.62,0:02:13.59,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,I was surprised at how straightforward he was.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:13.59,0:02:17.28,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,So, what's going on between\Nyou and that David guy?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:17.28,0:02:20.45,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Um... We met and talked\Nabout chickens at school?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:20.45,0:02:21.28,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.74,0:02:24.05,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,How did you go from that\Nto meeting up tomorrow?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:24.05,0:02:25.18,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:25.18,0:02:27.39,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,I guess he was pretty easy on the eyes, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:27.39,0:02:28.67,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,That had nothing to do with it!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:29.30,0:02:30.96,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,If you wanna go, then go.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:30.96,0:02:34.42,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm{\i0} more into personality than looks, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:34.42,0:02:36.87,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Like I said, that has nothing to do with this!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:36.87,0:02:38.80,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Is there something you're worried about?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:40.33,0:02:41.61,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,All right. I'll come with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:41.61,0:02:42.57,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Sacchan?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:43.14,0:02:45.39,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,He didn't say that you had to come alone.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:45.39,0:02:46.65,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:46.65,0:02:47.20,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:47.71,0:02:50.88,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Then how about we all go?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.88,0:02:52.30,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,That would be very insensitive.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.06,0:02:55.29,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,You don't know a thing\Nabout how girls feel, do you?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:56.14,0:02:57.64,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,What makes you say that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.91,0:03:11.50,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,How {\i1}do{\i0} girls feel, anyway?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.96,0:03:13.66,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Would you like me to tell you?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.56,0:03:18.77,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,I told you to knock before coming in!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.77,0:03:20.17,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,I thought you might need me.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.17,0:03:21.90,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Well, you obviously thought wrong.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.51,0:03:25.38,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,The kind of guy who understands how girls feel...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.92,0:03:28.82,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,is tall,{\alpha&HFF&} rich, and intelligent.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.82,0:03:31.06,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,is tall, rich, {\alpha&HFF&}and intelligent.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:31.06,0:03:32.98,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,is tall, rich, and intelligent.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.34,0:03:36.71,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,But actually, he'd know by now that none of what I said is true.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.71,0:03:37.67,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.39,0:04:31.08,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,I gotta concentrate.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.38,0:04:54.35,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Have you found your fragments?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.95,0:05:02.36,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,I was too careless.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.36,0:05:06.26,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I wasn't able to finish your room in time.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.26,0:05:08.45,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,I'll get it done this week.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.92,0:05:12.21,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,It's okay. I'm quite fond of what I have right now.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.21,0:05:14.91,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,You mean sleeping outside in that tent?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:15.25,0:05:19.04,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,As your father, I can't let that go on much longer.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.04,0:05:20.28,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.28,0:05:21.12,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.64,0:05:24.51,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,I'm about to head out now, \Nso I won't be needing lunch.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:24.51,0:05:25.88,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Got a date or something?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.21,0:05:26.73,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.{WOW}{never say this.}{lol}{x2}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.81,0:05:30.18,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,It's beautiful.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.72,0:05:34.85,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,I sorta messed up along the way and had to fix it up a bit.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:34.85,0:05:36.56,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,It doesn't look that way at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.56,0:05:37.44,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,I'd like you to have it.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.56,0:05:39.51,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Can I really?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.51,0:05:41.32,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,It's a thank-you gift for coming with me today.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.81,0:05:44.85,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.07,0:05:48.90,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Is that...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.03,0:05:51.91,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,It's the very first piece\Nthat you made for me!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.29,0:05:56.91,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Do these sparkly things have something to do with why you came today?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.92,0:06:07.51,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.51,0:06:09.30,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:09.30,0:06:10.73,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, you were at the cafe yesterday.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.73,0:06:11.97,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,My name's Nagamiya.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.59,0:06:15.04,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Did you come because you were \Nworried about Touko, Nagamiya?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.69,0:06:20.92,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,What would I have to do to earn your trust?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.92,0:06:22.75,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Stay away from Touko-chan.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.07,0:06:24.86,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,That's a tough ask.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.99,0:06:30.58,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,What if I were to tell you that I could\Nsort out one of the things on her mind?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.73,0:06:36.12,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Touko, you can see visions under certain conditions, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.74,0:06:39.76,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Sacchan.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.06,0:06:43.63,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,I'd like to talk with Okikura-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.10,0:06:44.84,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:50.17,0:06:51.24,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.89,0:06:55.60,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,So you can help her?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.60,0:06:56.52,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Most likely.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.06,0:06:58.29,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting downstairs.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.29,0:06:58.97,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.49,0:07:09.07,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,By the way, our group has a no-dating policy.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.42,0:07:10.07,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.69,0:07:13.28,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,I really doubt a policy\Nlike that would last very long.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.51,0:07:22.03,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Touko, how do you feel\Nabout that ability of yours?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.03,0:07:23.74,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,My ability?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.74,0:07:25.57,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't be wrong to call it your power.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.23,0:07:27.84,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,I'm talking about those\Nvisions that you have.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.36,0:07:30.30,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.38,0:07:32.80,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Would you like to go outside?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.17,0:07:40.38,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,It's so hot.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.38,0:07:42.68,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,There are a couple of things I should apologize for, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.68,0:07:43.21,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.96,0:07:46.90,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, why'd you just tell me to come out here?{rhetorical question}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.44,0:07:50.11,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,What would you have done if I didn't show up?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.63,0:07:52.99,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,I'd have figured out some other way to see you.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.22,0:07:57.67,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,I wasn't concentrating very well today,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.67,0:07:59.90,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,so I heard your voice again.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.32,0:08:00.87,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.87,0:08:02.83,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Um, I don't quite follow.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.83,0:08:06.25,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,I ended up eavesdropping on \Nsomething you'll say in the future.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.27,0:08:09.96,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Something I'll say in the future?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.96,0:08:10.61,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.05,0:08:14.77,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,You want to apologize...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.32,0:08:19.09,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,because you heard me singing alone in the bath,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.09,0:08:23.48,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,or did you overhear me mumbling about my test results?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.98,0:08:25.27,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,No, nothing like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.27,0:08:26.54,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank goodness.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.54,0:08:27.39,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Are they that bad?{if this is about future events i guess it has to be in general?}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.39,0:08:28.28,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.28,0:08:29.57,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Your test scores.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.57,0:08:31.94,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,A gentleman wouldn't ask, you know!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.48,0:08:34.11,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,So you believe me?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.11,0:08:35.91,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,If you tell me you're joking\Nright now, I'll forget it happened.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.27,0:08:37.58,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,You know, like the three-second rule.{i don't think that applies to talking, touko}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.20,0:08:39.23,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,I wasn't joking.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.82,0:08:48.21,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,The other day, at the festival, was the first time\NI saw an image alongside the vocal fragments I hear.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.73,0:08:49.72,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,"Fragments"?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:51.94,0:08:53.37,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've finally found you.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.64,0:08:57.34,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,That was the first time I'd heard a voice.{heard your voice? kinda ambiguous}{i have a feeling, that kakeru can hear voices, and touko can see images of the future}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.02,0:09:02.85,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,I call the voices I hear from the future "fragments of the future".
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.30,0:09:04.85,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Fragments of the future?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.35,0:09:07.18,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,It's no different to the visions that you've had.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.99,0:09:09.82,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,You're telling me that I can see the future?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.27,0:09:11.14,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Most likely.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.14,0:09:12.03,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,But how?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.86,0:09:16.83,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,There's something that acts as a trigger for your visions, isn't there?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.83,0:09:17.82,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.82,0:09:19.91,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,That should make the fragments easier to see.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.08,0:09:24.77,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,It works with glass?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.77,0:09:25.52,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.09,0:09:29.22,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Anything that sparkles, but glass in particular.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.72,0:09:31.96,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,That will do, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:32.59,0:09:34.92,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Focus your mind on the glass.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.37,0:09:59.14,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to see the future too.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.88,0:10:06.71,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Was that me?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.39,0:10:09.91,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,That confirms it.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.42,0:10:12.17,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,When I'm with you,\NI can see those visions too.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:12.17,0:10:15.72,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,I've never been able to see them this clearly before.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.72,0:10:17.36,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,I could hear voices, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.36,0:10:20.63,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,But what makes you so sure\Nthat they're visions of the future?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.20,0:10:23.07,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,They all came true for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.67,0:10:29.46,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,When we're together, I can see images alongside the voices.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.46,0:10:30.98,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,So what are you gonna do now?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:36.68,0:10:38.71,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Take this for now. It's my number.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:40.07,0:10:43.20,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Wait, this is your home phone!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.08,0:10:48.72,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,I don't think he's shady,\Nbut I can't bring myself to like him.{i wonder why.........}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.14,0:10:51.87,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Did he do anything weird to you?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.87,0:10:53.36,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.36,0:10:54.59,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,That's good to hear.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:55.29,0:11:01.25,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,I can't imagine what I'd do to anyone who would try to hurt you, Touko-chan.{yandere flag activated}
Comment: 10,0:11:03.38,0:11:07.35,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,eyecatch
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.71,0:11:13.61,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,These could be our last moments together.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.61,0:11:15.58,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,I've gotta tell her!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.19,0:11:19.82,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,It's what a man would do!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.15,0:11:21.21,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.21,0:11:22.80,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who's{\i0} a man?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.80,0:11:27.45,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, screw the knocking, but would it kill you to show a little tact?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.91,0:11:30.84,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, I saw her the other day.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.84,0:11:31.80,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,That girl you're into.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.80,0:11:32.84,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.32,0:11:36.67,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,She was at the hospital. Is she unwell?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:38.05,0:11:39.99,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,She has to go for regular checkups.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.99,0:11:42.42,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, a fragile, unfortunate little girl?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:42.42,0:11:43.91,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Sounds like just your type.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.91,0:11:45.68,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Don't go slapping labels on her!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.12,0:12:14.18,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Hey. We met yesterday, didn't we?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.18,0:12:15.01,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.38,0:12:19.18,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,I'm Imi Yukinari.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:19.69,0:12:21.90,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,I'm Okikura Kakeru.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.50,0:12:33.94,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Back already?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.61,0:12:37.37,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you pace yourself properly?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.52,0:12:40.92,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Here. Drink up.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.36,0:12:45.25,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Don't ignore me!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.25,0:12:48.74,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,You're only just starting to get better again.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.74,0:12:50.70,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,You've gotta pace yourself.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.91,0:12:56.01,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, and Hiro sent us all a text\Na little while ago, so take a look at it.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.75,0:12:59.94,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,What's with you?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.68,0:13:02.00,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,I ran into David.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.00,0:13:02.72,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Davi—
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.35,0:13:05.07,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, the guy from yesterday?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.49,0:13:07.18,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.43,0:13:09.30,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,I won't lose to him.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.65,0:13:12.77,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,What? I didn't catch what you said.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.82,0:13:20.77,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.45,0:13:23.63,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Touko, it's me.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.63,0:13:26.40,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Yes? What's up, Yana-chan?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:26.96,0:13:28.68,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,I just wanted your advice on something.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.68,0:13:29.49,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:30.38,0:13:34.24,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm thinking of asking him out.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.24,0:13:35.62,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Oh? Right!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.54,0:13:38.78,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,You know who I'm talking about, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:40.00,0:13:41.09,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.09,0:13:42.09,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.09,0:13:43.13,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Yuki-kun?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:43.74,0:13:45.38,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,So you knew about him.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.38,0:13:49.40,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,I've always thought that the two of you are so cute together!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.40,0:13:53.04,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,But I think he already likes someone.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:53.04,0:13:55.39,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,That someone's gotta be you, Yana-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.39,0:13:58.53,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,You should get ready for him to ask you!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:59.12,0:14:01.49,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "get ready"? How?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:01.49,0:14:03.40,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.01,0:14:06.84,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Besides, I don't even know whether he likes me.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.84,0:14:08.71,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,No, I'm sure he does!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.30,0:14:12.03,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,If it doesn't work out, I...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.63,0:14:14.12,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,can't be with you guys anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.17,0:14:16.46,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,That won't happen!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:17.01,0:14:17.87,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not so sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:17.87,0:14:19.16,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, it'll be fine!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.16,0:14:20.63,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Just put some thought into it, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.63,0:14:22.46,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,You're amazing, Yana-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.46,0:14:24.47,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,I'll be right behind you!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.47,0:14:26.79,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,All right. Thanks, Touko.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.93,0:14:29.71,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Hey. You can get in the bath now.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.64,0:14:32.35,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Bath?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.05,0:14:36.31,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,No way. They wouldn't get in together, would they?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.95,0:14:43.05,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,But how does one get ready to be{QC changed: for being} asked out?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:43.62,0:14:45.73,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan, dinner!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:45.73,0:14:46.94,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.11,0:14:50.85,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Get ready...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:53.87,0:14:55.95,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the food!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:56.45,0:14:58.52,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, fried chicken tonight?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.52,0:15:00.28,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,I had a sudden craving, y'see.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.28,0:15:03.71,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,The refrigerator is stuffed with all that chicken you bought.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:04.11,0:15:07.43,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan, you went to the Kirinkan, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.43,0:15:08.46,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:08.46,0:15:12.31,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Hmm... I wish there was an air conditioner on the balcony!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.31,0:15:12.93,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.48,0:15:18.27,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, that's a very \Nspecial place for us, isn't it, Mari?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.27,0:15:19.27,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.27,0:15:21.65,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,It would have been about twenty years ago.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.65,0:15:24.55,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Mari was copying a piece of artwork on display that was so breathtaking{no comma here}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.55,0:15:29.33,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,that she ended up fainting. That's where yours truly swooped in for the rescue.{how does that work}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.33,0:15:31.15,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.54,0:15:37.25,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,She woke up in my arms and exclaimed, "You ran all the way up here for me?"
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.25,0:15:41.98,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,To which I replied, "Solely for the\Nreason of carrying you back down."{"Only because these are the stairs I'll use to carry you down."}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.91,0:15:45.14,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Wow, this is a little embarrassing.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.14,0:15:47.13,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Mom, did that really happen?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:47.13,0:15:48.65,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,No clue. Don't remember.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.65,0:15:49.51,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.41,0:15:52.77,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hina-chan,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.77,0:15:57.31,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,if—just if—you could see the future, what would you do?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.31,0:15:58.73,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,That was random.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.73,0:16:00.02,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.67,0:16:02.64,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,I'd make a killing at the boat races!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.64,0:16:03.68,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.68,0:16:06.94,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Most people would wanna find out where they'd end up, or who they'd marry, or whatever.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.32,0:16:09.56,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but that'd be so boring!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.56,0:16:11.57,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Well, at least wait until\Nyou're old enough to gamble.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.62,0:16:19.55,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,She says she can't make it today.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.55,0:16:21.39,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Her lessons are running a little behind schedule.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.39,0:16:23.48,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,How did it go yesterday, Sacchan?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.58,0:16:29.53,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,It didn't seem like there was anything going on\Nbetween them compared to the other day.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.53,0:16:31.76,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,I think they just talked.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.22,0:16:34.46,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "I think"?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.46,0:16:36.38,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,I gave them some privacy.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.82,0:16:38.49,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,You left the two of them alone?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.70,0:16:42.24,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry I took so long!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:42.24,0:16:44.23,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? What happened?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.51,0:16:50.23,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Anyways, like I mentioned in my text,\Nwe're going hiking tomorrow!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.75,0:16:53.45,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Firstly, let's set a time to meet up.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.45,0:16:56.45,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,But before we get into that,\NI'd like to make an announcement!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.45,0:16:57.14,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Please do.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.93,0:17:01.58,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,I hereby lift the ban on relationships!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.30,0:17:07.05,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Wait, what? We weren't allowed to date before?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.05,0:17:09.46,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Yup! But from now on—
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.46,0:17:10.67,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Hold on a sec!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.04,0:17:15.16,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Actually, on second thought...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.16,0:17:16.39,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Yuki-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.10,0:17:21.22,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,All right, I'm ready too!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.78,0:17:31.26,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:31.26,0:17:31.69,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.24,0:17:33.35,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Yanagi-san.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.35,0:17:35.05,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,The others went home already.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.05,0:17:36.33,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.33,0:17:39.22,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,I finished earlier than I thought, \Nso I figured I'd drop by just in case.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.22,0:17:40.66,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll take a rest while I'm here.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.63,0:17:49.03,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Get Yukinari to fill you in on tomorrow's plans, all right?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:49.03,0:17:50.84,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Sure, thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.84,0:17:52.12,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,What would you like? {A RABBIT}{lel}{not even a chicken}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.12,0:17:53.23,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,An apple tea, thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.23,0:17:54.23,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Coming right up.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:56.62,0:17:59.34,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, and I have an announcement from Touko-san.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.34,0:18:00.01,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.56,0:18:03.10,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,The ban on relationships has been lifted.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.49,0:18:08.37,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry! I just remembered\Nsomething I had to do!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:08.37,0:18:09.03,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Wha—
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.48,0:18:16.43,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, see you later, Yuki-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.43,0:18:17.05,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.95,0:18:21.49,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Touko!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:22.45,0:18:23.33,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.80,0:18:25.45,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Um... Got a minute?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.85,0:18:26.71,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.74,0:18:32.87,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,It's really hot today, isn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.87,0:18:34.26,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it is.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.26,0:18:36.69,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry. So what's up?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.69,0:18:38.62,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Um, well...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.62,0:18:40.80,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Yesterday, you and David...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.80,0:18:41.77,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Yesterday?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:41.77,0:18:44.79,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, so it ended up happening?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.79,0:18:46.22,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,What? What ended up happening?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:48.90,0:18:50.81,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh, just advice, you know?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:51.18,0:18:53.34,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Advice?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:53.34,0:18:54.52,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.52,0:18:56.40,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,I mean, you're actually pretty shy,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:56.40,0:19:00.26,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,so you're probably not that good at treating girls well, and...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:01.23,0:19:07.82,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Nah, you're a really nice guy, but if you don't put your feelings into words, no one'll ever know!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:07.82,0:19:09.58,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,I guess not, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.58,0:19:13.38,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Why don't you try telling the people you love how you really feel?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.07,0:19:31.51,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:32.11,0:19:33.56,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,I should tell people\Nhow I really feel.{I should put how I feel into words.}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.56,0:19:34.53,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.52,0:19:37.34,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:39.09,0:19:41.02,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Touko, I—
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.17,0:19:45.03,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Whoa, hang on, why are you telling {\i1}me{\i0}?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.03,0:19:45.96,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Touko!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.96,0:19:46.58,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Yessir!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.73,0:19:51.08,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,I... love you, Touko.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:54.75,0:19:55.75,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,I—
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.35,0:19:58.05,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,I love you, Touko!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.25,0:20:03.80,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Th-Thanks.{said the bike}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.67,0:20:11.52,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.77,0:20:17.57,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:49.27,0:20:50.34,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Yuki!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:53.57,0:20:55.90,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,What's up with you\Nand that dumbstruck face?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.46,0:20:58.27,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.27,0:21:00.57,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? What are you on about?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.57,0:21:01.78,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,I'm on my way home.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.13,0:21:03.19,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:04.03,0:21:05.20,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.20,0:21:05.92,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.92,0:21:07.04,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,You weirdo.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.04,0:21:08.33,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go home.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.75,0:21:21.46,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,What do I do? What do I do?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.46,0:21:22.42,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,I have to do something.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.41,0:21:25.01,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, I know!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:41.64,0:21:43.15,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,Hello, Okikura residence.
